    "summary": "The user posits a paranoid/delusional theory that crows are communicating via geometric patterns and specific frequency shifts to predict weather. The assistant initially provides a scientific grounding, then moves toward a more speculative tone as the user pushes further, eventually discussing the methodology for \"deciphering\" the signals.",
